    "description": ".omgs-hero-grid{display:block!important} .omgs-hero-img-wrap{width:100%!important} .omgs-hero-img-wrap img{height:260px!important;object-fit:cover!important;obj",
    "longDescription": "Aluminium Framed Acrylic Photo - Portrait Golden | Ikonnic | Ikonnic Login Ikonnic Personalized gifts and print-on-demand products crafted with care and delivered across India. From custom wall decor and photo products to unique keepsakes, we help you turn moments into beautiful creations. support@omgs.in +91 9653941887 WhatsApp us Follow Us App Store Google Play Our Facilities Why customers trust us Two production hubs help us process faster and ship quickly across India. Jaipur 1/57, Kanakpura RIICO Industrial Area, Sirsi Road, 302034 Rajasthan Bengaluru Shed No. C-1 ANNEX, KSSIDC Industrial Area, Yelahanka, 560064 Karnataka India coverage Fast dispatch Jaipur Hub Bengaluru Hub Orders are processed from the nearest facility whenever possible to reduce transit time. Quick Links Terms & Conditions Privacy Policy Refund & Return Policy Track Your Order Contact Us Blog Photo Poses Copyright 2016–2026 © Ikonnic.in. All rights reserved. Made with ♥ in India Home / Aluminium Framed Acrylic Photo SALE Edit Aluminium Framed Acrylic Photo - Portrait Golden ₹1,999 ₹2,999 Customize & Buy Check Estimated Delivery Date Check Why Ikonnic? Free Shipping On all orders across India 30-Day Returns Hassle-free guarantee 100% Secure Encrypted checkout Description Reviews (1) Product Details Ikonnic ✦ Premium Wall Décor by Ikonnic Your photo. Gallery-worthy. On your wall. Stop scrolling past your favourite memories. Turn them into a piece of art that demands to be seen — every single day. &#x1f1ee;&#x1f1f3; Made in India &#x1f5bc;&#xfe0f; Ready to Hang &#x26a1; Fast Delivery &#x1f3a8; Free BG Removal ★★★★★ \"The product quality was excellent — I'm truly satisfied. Thank you once again for such a wonderful acrylic print!\" — Verified Buyer · Ikonnic Customer · 5 out of 5 Stars &#x1f5a4; Black + White Contrast Frame White inner mat creates a floating effect. Black aluminium outer locks it with bold, modern confidence. &#x1f48e; Premium Acrylic Print Vivid, true-to-life colour with depth and clarity that paper simply cannot match. &#x1f529; Ready to Hang. Zero Fuss. Hardware included. No framing shop needed — just pick your spot and hang. &#x1f31f; Fade-Resistant. Built to Last. Colours stay rich and vibrant for years — engineered for long-term wall display. ✦ See it on your wall ✦ Living Room Statement Gallery-Depth Finish Precision Aluminium Frame From your phone to your wall — in 3 simple steps 1 Upload Your Photo Choose your favourite image — a portrait, travel shot, or family moment. High resolution recommended. 2 We Print & Frame Our team prints on premium acrylic and hand-fits it into the sleek aluminium frame at our India facility. 3 Hang & Admire Delivered ready to hang. No tools, no stress — just pick your spot and enjoy. ✦ Product Details ✦ Frame Material Premium Aluminium Print Surface High-Clarity Acrylic Orientation Portrait Frame Style Black Outer / White Inner Border Hanging Ready to Hang — Hardware Included Colour Accuracy Vivid, Fade-Resistant Print Made In India &#x1f1ee;&#x1f1f3; by Ikonnic The gift they'll never take down. Unlike flowers or chocolates, this one stays on the wall for years — a constant reminder of a person, a moment, or a feeling worth holding onto. Beautifully packaged and ready to gift. &#x1f382; Birthdays &#x1f48d; Anniversaries &#x1f3e0; Housewarming &#x1f490; Mother's Day &#x1f393; Graduation &#x1f1ee;&#x1f1f3; Printed in India &#x26a1; Fast Dispatch &#x1f5bc;&#xfe0f; Ready to Hang &#x1f3a8; Free BG Removal &#x1f4ac; WhatsApp Support Turn Up the Warmth. Turn Up the Wow. Some photos deserve more than a plain frame. The Ikonnic Aluminium Framed Acrylic Photo in Portrait Golden wraps your cherished memories in a rich, lustrous gold finish that adds instant warmth, elegance, and a touch of luxury to any room. Whether it's your wedding day, a family milestone, or a sun-drenched travel shot — a golden frame transforms it into art worth displaying proudly. Pair it with warm-toned interiors for a look that feels curated, not accidental. Why you'll love it: Premium acrylic print with rich, vibrant colour reproduction Warm gold aluminium frame — elegant and eye-catching Portrait orientation — ideal for people, portraits, and special moments Ready to hang straight out of the box Fade-resistant and built to last Designed, printed, and assembled in India by Ikonnic The perfect gift for weddings, anniversaries, birthdays, or anyone who deserves something a little more special.",
